    <item>
      <title>“你的身体，我的选择”：选举日后网上对女性的骚扰激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/online-abuse-toward-women-spikes-after-trump-wins-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[战略对话研究所称，自美国大选以来，针对女性的网络辱骂、骚扰和仇恨激增，在X和TikTok等平台上，“你的身体，我的选择”和“回厨房去”等短语泛滥。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/online-abuse-toward-women-spikes-after-trump-wins-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
